name: ⚠️ Remove copyrighted content
description: This form is for copyright owners to remove copyrighted content from this repository.
title: '[⚠️ Takedown Request]: '
labels: ['bug']

body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        Please take your time to read the entirety of this, and fill out all required boxes. Please be ready to prove that you have the rights to the affected content as well.

  - type: input
    attributes:
      label: Affected channel numbers
      description: Please specify the numbers of the affected channels to proceed.
      placeholder: '5, 21, 56'
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    attributes:
      label: Contact details
      placeholder: 'Please provide a way to contact you to proceed. For example, john@example.com.'
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        Legal disclaimer: I do not host any of the content stored on here. This is simply just a collection of free-to-air streams from other websites, which I do not control. By submitting a takedown request here, you should also note that other lists may still include links to the copyrighted streams.

  - type: checkboxes
    attributes:
      label: Please confirm the following
      options:
        - label: I've read the legal disclaimer above
          required: true
        - label: I am the copyright owner or I have gained permission from the copyright owner to take this down
          required: true
        - label: I understand that if I fail to provide information within the request, it may be closed
          required: true
